                "What are the dominant spatial patterns of major pollutants at regional and urban scales?",
                "How do these patterns evolve across daily, seasonal and multi‑year timescales?",
                "Which data sources (satellite, ground stations, emission inventories) and GIS techniques best support high‑resolution, time‑stamped grid visualisations?"
